title: Broken Rhythms
tooltip: universal property: characters can't take the same action twice in a row
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

While on a [[plane]] with this property, a creature can't use the exact same [[approach]] twice in a row. This means if a character makes an attempt using "Force," they can't use Force again until they make an attempt using a different approach.